{"tid":2120747,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"朝早不定期比胃氣頂住幾年，好辛苦好困擾，求助","createTime":"2020-07-23T01:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T02:24:59.000Z","uid":337322,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3c4d6d765c70c94dc6ebbbc23de1cd43ea8180","tid":2120747,"uid":337322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:17:37.000Z","msg":"一朝早起身係咁<br />\n啲氣卡住喺喉嚨<br />\n作嘔感覺，自己比較抗拒嘔，會抑住<br />\n要靠飲半啖水排解，唔係次次得，如果唔得，之後會好辛苦咁咳出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吞口水無助排氣，有時反而怕辛苦果陣吞得好急，更加多胃氣<br />\n直到一刻排完晒所有氣之後就可以即刻冇事<br />\n<br />\n2年前睇過中醫，好返過一排又出返黎。睇西醫又比唔到咩長久紓緩嘅strategies我<em></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">每次係咁真係好辛苦......,有冇人介紹到啲簡單準備到嘅食療/醫生/方法？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以下係少少background：<br />\n會夜瞓早起；<br />\n已戒可樂/碳酸飲品；<br />\n因為慣出街食，三餐比較唔健康；<br />\n星期六日9成9冇依個問題，多數返工先會，諗過會唔會係緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf11e1fb44903cc5aa49b6e7c56359093d738f6","tid":2120747,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:18:27.000Z","msg":"打少d j"},{"pid":"9adf15637f4027e6e21787ff93dea8d49291e3e8","tid":2120747,"uid":13767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:19:23.000Z","msg":"唔夠訓+緊張"},{"pid":"e6386454f7e05b2e78523ae91d80c360fdb5544f","tid":2120747,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:23:05.000Z","msg":"飲半L水"},{"pid":"b06e5b5642810267be251095413b09477ca9e7c1","tid":2120747,"uid":337322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6386454f7e05b2e78523ae91d80c360fdb5544f","tid":2120747,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:23:05.000Z","msg":"飲半L水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:25:56.000Z","msg":"依排返工都有意識地飲多啲水，至少一日飲夠1.5升"},{"pid":"ca3434c2046c37bec58727020fc39eaeb2a35fce","tid":2120747,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b06e5b5642810267be251095413b09477