0Z","msg":"其實三餐定唔定時食都有關"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:43:27.000Z","msg":"有冇少少提議三餐可以食咩？<br />\n<br />\n唔介意麥皮溝水咁清淡，但真心返工好難準備到太複雜嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食肉好似好多氣，我自己就鍾意菜多過肉,但無奈出面餐廳都係多油多鹽守肉少菜<br />\n<br />\n如果晚餐自煮+第日帶飯返工做午餐，有冇啲suggestion?"},{"pid":"97d146df9864b4d8e16b4f5a043934ee626e5e0e","tid":2120747,"uid":33125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:47:49.000Z","msg":"飲水分離+食野咬到好瀾先吞"},{"pid":"f39c235d22c43bcbbe4b61757deb1d0c16f55369","tid":2120747,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b7c6c0bd74206fa7247362054cb09c7d9616a22e","tid":2120747,"uid":337322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9adf15637f4027e6e21787ff93dea8d49291e3e8","tid":2120747,"uid":13767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:19:23.000Z","msg":"唔夠訓+緊張"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有戒色 但夜瞓真心會改架喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:49:32.000Z","msg":"關戒色咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a11ef63345bb651011465913cf062404937a74c","tid":2120747,"uid":282478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:49:39.000Z","msg":"壓力大"},{"pid":"b6f17d6eb4b4d2dfb1c44ec87743dbf9a93ed6a1","tid":2120747,"uid":51250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:52:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會夜瞓早起；<br />\n已戒可樂/碳酸飲品；<br />\n因為慣出街食，三餐比較唔健康；<br />\n星期六日9成9冇依個問題，多數返工先會</blockquote><br />\n有機會係weekday消化不良啦<br />\n出街食嘢食少啲唔好食咁飽+食慢啲<br />\n星期六日有得瞓耐啲個人輕鬆啲消化能力都好啲所以有機會冇事"},{"pid":"17249470638cb41f27f31d7656a4716aba7144a9","tid":2120747,"uid":82815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:53:37.000Z","msg":"早啲瞓<br />\n最好朝早飲啲暖水<br />\n解決壓力<br />\n照胃鏡<br />\n利申過來人"},{"pid":"3f353d0e4624b1eddfceb94fae960d5f818b7102","tid":2120747,"uid":82815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s